The Testing Support Module
--------------------------

<h4>Overview</h4>
The Oracle Tools Testing Support module provides a number of extensions to simplify
testing concurrent and distributed applications.

As this module makes significant use of the concept of Deferred References, we recommend
reading the [Introduction to Deferred References](../core/deferreds.html) for initial
examples and background information.

<h4>Distribution</h4>

The Oracle Tools Testing Support module is distributed as a single jar
called: `oracle-tools-testing-support-${project.version}.jar`


The [maven.java.net](https://maven.java.net) artifact information is as follows:

*   Maven Group Id: `${project.groupId}`
*   Maven Artifact Id: `oracle-tools-testing-support`
*   Maven Version: `${project.version}`

Alternatively you can downlown directly from: <img src="../images/external-link.png" alt="External Link" height="10" width="10" align="top"/> [oracle-tools-testing-support-${project.version}.jar](https://maven.java.net/service/local/artifact/maven/redirect?r=${repository}&g=com.oracle.tools&a=oracle-tools-testing-support&v=${project.version}&e=jar)

